      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUDDEN SURPRISE (8) missed the frame last time when fourth (22.96) at The Gardens but prior to that had two placings in a row. Form here sound including two wins. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Ready to return to form. AVA'S MILO (4) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (25.24) at this track over 431m. Can feature again. MUGGLE (2) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 4/5 win two back (19.76) at this track. Expected to do much better this time. ROY THE BOY (1) warrants respect although new to this track.",
